<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-285] DNE: incorrect reference to &quot;lfs rmdir&quot;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-285</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the Lustre operations manual, the section (&quot;14.8.1. Removing a MDT from the File System&quot;) describing DNE makes reference to a command &quot;lfs rmdir&quot; when deleting a remote directory entry. This command does not exist; instead, one should invoke the normal rmdir command to remove a DNE remote directory.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="30082">LUDOC-285</key>
