                            <comment id="193067" author="adilger" created="Fri, 21 Apr 2017 19:06:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Instead of &quot;lfs rmdir&quot; there is the &quot;lfs rm_entry&quot; command that allows deleting a directory entry for a remote DNE directory on an MDT that is no longer available.  &quot;rm -r&quot; should be used if the remote MDT is still available.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
